ic\ntransition. However, the magnetocaloric effect (MCE) is expected to be lower in\nErVO3 due to the weak (Er-V) exchange coupling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Nov 2022 17:21:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-15"}
