dic knowledge and current events\n-- crucial to understanding the production and consumption of knowledge in the\ndigital age.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Nov 2022 18:36:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 May 2023 17:17:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-15"}
