NER spectra obey\nessentially the same \\lxo\\ relation as Seyfert 2s, suggesting their line\nemission is produced by AGN activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Nov 2022 19:00:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-15"}
