posed schemes designed based on the mutual\ninformation metric can suppress the echo interference from the communication\nusers effectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2022 04:22:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2023 15:43:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-12"}
